Interface InlineCodeSnippet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

    public interface InlineCodeSnippet
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Inline Code Snippet'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Snippet Position
    • Snippet Name
    • Snippet Code
    • Lang
    See Also:
    GuigenPackage.getInlineCodeSnippet()
